              Customizable Dashboard Layouts
            </h3>
            <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
              Dashboard widgets can be rearranged to prioritize metrics most
              relevant to your role and responsibilities. Operations managers
              might emphasize team utilization rates and appointment volume
              trends. Sales leaders likely prioritize conversion metrics and
              revenue forecasting. Support directors may focus on customer
              appointment patterns and response time analytics. Custom layouts
              ensure each user sees their critical metrics prominently without
              scrolling through irrelevant data. Widget configurations save
              automatically, so your personalized dashboard appears consistently
              across sessions and devices. This customization makes dashboard
              useful rather than overwhelming by focusing attention on metrics
              that actually drive decision-making in your specific role.
            </p>
